sewing machine and lifts her
family out of poverty.

00:00:11.910 --> 00:00:14.210
And who wouldn't love
that story?

00:00:14.210 --> 00:00:15.120
We all love it.

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.950
And so about 20 years ago, a lot
