00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:07.160
[APPLAUSE]

00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:07.890
HUGH SINCLAIR: Lovely.

00:01:07.890 --> 00:01:09.330
Thank you very much.

00:01:09.330 --> 00:01:11.590
Great honor to be in the
