00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:21.360
You all vaguely know
what it is.

00:01:21.360 --> 00:01:23.690
Has anyone done any investments
in microfinance,

00:01:23.690 --> 00:01:25.560
in Kiva, those sorts
of things, funds?

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.570
Yeah, OK.

00:01:26.570 --> 00:01:30.380
So this is probably going
to be kind of sobering.

00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:34.190
I'm an economist originally, and
former investment banker.

00:01:34.190 --> 00:01:38.070
I have an MBA from IESE Business
School in Barcelona.

00:01:38.070 --> 00:01:41.750
And I was, I believe, the
last employee at Enron.

00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:43.890
I joined two weeks before
